<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="E" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Earnest2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Earnest,</orth> subst. seriousness, true meaning; opposed to jest: <cit><quote>did you perceive her e.?</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.1.163" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. II, 1, 163</bibl></cit> (quibble). <cit><quote>it was a passion of e.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 4.3.172" default="NO" valid="yes">As IV, 3, 172</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>now your jest is e.</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 2.2.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. II, 2, 24</bibl></cit> (quibble. <cit><quote>in e.:</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.5.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. II, 5, 13</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. err 4.2.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 2, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 5.1.197" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 1, 197</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.2.277" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 2, 277</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.656" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 656</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 5.3.100" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 3, 100</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.334" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 334</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.1.22" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 V, 1, 22</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 1.3.106" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 3, 106</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 1.277" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. I, 277</bibl>. <cit><quote>in good e.:</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.2.29" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 2, 29</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.3.26" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 26</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 4.1.192" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 192</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.150" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 150</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.1.168" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 1, 168</bibl> (Q <emph>so God save me</emph>). <cit><quote>in most profound e.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 5.1.198" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 1, 198</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>